Judy McBurney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judy_McBurney 0 Judith McBurney (19 May 1948 – 1 December 2018) was an Australian actress, voice-over artist and model. She played Nurse Tania Livingston in The Young Doctors and Pixie Mason in Prisoner. Judith_McBurney ( 19_May_1948 – 1_December_2018 ) was an_Australian_actress , voice-over_artist_and_model .
